---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../components/Tagline.astro';
---

<Layout title="Manifesto - Wellmade" description="We build products that matter, built by people who care, for people who deserve better.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">We're tired.</h1>
      <div class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 space-y-4">
        <p>Tired of watching money burn on products nobody asked for.</p>
        <p>Tired of features built for stakeholders, not users.</p>
        <p>Tired of "MVPs" that are neither minimal nor viable.</p>
        <p>Tired of projects that ship once and rot.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Something Got Lost -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">We believe something got lost.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Somewhere between the briefs and the backlogs, between the specs and the sprints, we forgot why we build.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We build for people. Real people with real problems who deserve tools that actually work for them.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed">
        Not tools that look good in demos. Not tools that tick boxes. Tools that make someone's day a little easier, a little better.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- So We Made A Choice -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">So we made a choice.</h2>
      <div class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body space-y-4 mb-8">
        <p>We don't build to fill timesheets.</p>
        <p>We don't build to impress committees.</p>
        <p>We don't build what's asked if what's asked doesn't make sense.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary">We build products that matter.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">This is how we work.</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Lean.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">No waste. No theater. No features nobody will use. Every line of code earns its place.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Pragmatic.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">What works beats what's trendy. We choose boring technology that ships over shiny technology that stalls.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Builders.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">We don't hand over documents. We hand over working products. We're in the code, in the pixels, in the problem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Delivering.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Ideas are cheap. Shipped products aren't. We finish what we start.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- We've Done This Before -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">We've done this before.</h2>
      <div class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body space-y-4 mb-8">
        <p>For solo founders building their first product.</p>
        <p>For agencies who needed builders they could trust.</p>
        <p>For enterprises where compliance and security aren't optional.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">One-person startups to GSK-level rigor. Same standards. Same care.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Compass -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Our compass.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We want the people who use what we build to feel understood.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Not impressed. Not overwhelmed. <span class="text-accent font-bold">Understood.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        Like someone actually listened. Like someone gave a damn about how they work, what they struggle with, what they actually need.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium mt-8">That's the bar. That's what we chase.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- We Don't Compromise -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">We don't compromise.</h2>
      <div class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body space-y-4 mb-8">
        <p>Not on quality.</p>
        <p>Not on integrity.</p>
        <p>Not on doing the right thing when the easier thing is right there.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        We'd rather build less and build it right than ship more and regret it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Promise -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Our promise.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We want to be proud of everything we've ever built.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Every product. Every feature. Every line.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        If we can't stand behind it, we don't ship it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Innovation With A Vision -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-accent font-cursive text-3xl mb-6">Innovation with a vision.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-12">This is ours:</h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold leading-relaxed">
        Products that matter, built by people who care, for people who deserve better.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Let's talk
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Tagline text="Wellmade. Lean builders. We deliver." />
</Layout>
